name: Rival Species
summary: In the far distant future of the 40th millennium behind the stars there is only war. Enter the universe of WARHAMMER 40,000 and play a mighty warrior for one out of an ever growing list of rival species. A large PvP team multiplayer mod for Half-Life that plays similary to Battlefield/Battlefront, based on the Game's Workshop property. Eventually Exterminatus, A sequel for the Source Engine would be made

name: Welcome to... Chichester 2: Part II - No Regrets For the Future
summary: Taking place on the second day of your holiday, you start reminiscing with Grendel Jinx about how you two first met. Inevitably, the discussion turns to a dark period in both your lives when tragedy and revenge nearly destroy your "friendship" with each other.
storyline:
Taking place on the second day of the protagonist's holiday, who wakes up with a nasty headache, which is not helped by the presence of the protagonist's "nemesis" - the megalomaniacal, kleptomaniac and cake mix loving Grendel Jinx. Whilst waiting for breakfast to be served, talk to turns to how you both met and eventually the conversation veers into a period where your budding "friendship" was nearly permanently severed.

Suffering a string of defeats by Grendel, following by an unauthorised beating by her bodyguards, the protagonist's time is spent in the local hospital wondering what went wrong. Eventually coming to a very undesirable conclusion, the protagonist's secretary is tasked with finding out whether the protagonists' supposition is correct or not.

Meanwhile, Grendel gets news that her bodyguards have been killed, and with all evidence pointing to the protagonist, she sets out for revenge.

name: Power Guy World
summary: Power Guy World is a 30 exit SMW romhack created by LucasMegaStriker as a tribute to the Vtuber "Power Guy".
storyline: Power Guy is a video game character, who together with his dog Merf, live in a small computer, playing games all day. But then, an evil group of hackers broke into their home and kidnapped Merf! Now it's up to Power Guy to save his best friend by getting into the world of the internet!

name: What the Bat?
summary: You have baseball bats for hands - now go! In this surprising VR comedy, you play through a series of silly physical mini-games that make you laugh, cry and even pet nice animals.
storyline: A wise man once said: If all you have are bats for hands, everything feels like a baseball.

name: Ace wo Nerae!
summary: A tennis game for the Super Famicom based on the 1970s manga and anime of the same name.

name: The Deal
summary: A Doom II WAD.

name: Nightmare Kart: The Old Karts
summary: An upcoming free expansion to Nightmare Kart with a brand new mini-campaign, racers, karts, tracks, power-ups, and game modes.

name: 100 Kills Challenge
summary: "100 Kills Challenge" is an intense and fast-paced first-person tactical shooting game. The only goal in the game is to kill 100 enemies as much as possible within the specified time to win.

name: Montezuma's Revenge
summary:
This is the official version of the 80's classic game Montezuma's Revenge rebooted by the original developer. It's the classic puzzle solving action adventure platformer you loved in your youth.

Unlike the switch port, this port adds a "Modern Mode" visuals.

name: Yokai Dungeon
summary: Yokai have just interrupted the lantern festival, it's up to Tanuki and his friends to save the day. Push blocks to crush the pesky yokai, explore randomly generated dungeons, and dive into beatiful Japanese folklore.

name: Electro Havoc
summary: Electro Havoc: A retro twin-stick shooter set in a neon-charged battleground where you'll face waves of geometric foes. Lure more enemies into debris fields to trigger chain reactions, and grab power-ups to boost your multipliers.

name: Nautic XP
summary: Nautic XP. The ultimate ship simulation! Navigate realistic sceneries with advanced physics, real seamarks, and dynamic weather. Various ships with detailed systems. Realistic navigation & AI ship traffic. Challenging missions: rescue, transport & towing. Set sail now!

name: Echoes in the Storm
summary: Investigate a series of brutal crimes in a remote Arctic town in this psychological horror experience steeped in oppressive atmosphere. Step into the shoes of Detective James Northland and face the terrifying beast threatening to shatter your sanity in this chilling tale of mystery.

name: Hotel Transylvania 3: Monsters Overboard
summary: Dracula, Mavis and their monster friends are marooned on the mysterious Lost Islands – and only you, in command of lovable little creatures, the Impa, can save them! Explore the islands, discover new Impa abilities, and rescue Frankenstein, Murray and Wayne from fearsome enemies. But hurry – the Drac-Pack’s lives are at stake!

name: Way of the Hunter: Christensen Arms Pack
summary: Way of the Hunter has partnered with Christensen Arms to bring you two iconic hunting rifles.

name: Chowder: Rump-A-Thump
summary: Chowder is helping Mung Daal with three different items, thumpster,cutterfly,and spinzle with his rump(end). There are different foods for you to get for the orders. There are lots of hazards for you to dodge,avoid,and keep away.

name: Hunter Hitman
summary: Hunt or be hunted. Execute stealth kills and survive in this action-packed assassin game.

name: Merge Games Horror Bundle
summary: What do dark Nordic fables, intergalactic cruises and Lovecraftian gore all have in common? Gruesome, gory and ghoulish monsters! Dive into the horror-themed worlds of Bramble: The Mountain King, Morbid: The Seven Acolytes and Slaycation Paradise - if you dare!

name: Escape 2088
summary: Escape2088 is an old-school point & click escape room game with modern 3D graphics! Explore a futuristic environment and use your problem-solving skills to set yourself free! Careful observation of the surroundings will help you discover hidden clues, solve logic puzzles and escape in time!

name: DCS World: NS 430 Navigation System for SA342 Gazelle by Eagle Dynamics, Polychop Simulations
summary: The NS 430 for the SA342 Gazelle module integrates the NS 430 panel directly into the SA342 Gazelle cockpit (not as a pop-up display).

name: SushiCat: Bento
summary: Sushi, cats, and endless combos! Dive into a unique blend of roguelike deckbuilding and strategic tile placement! Fresh, fun, and oh-so-tasty – SushiCat: Bento is here!

name: Fight,to the last
summary: This is a 2D dungeon rogue shooting game. Players can kill enemies to stick a variety of dropped weapons, free combination, through a variety of different combinations to define their own attack mode.

name: Banners of Ruin: Iris
summary: Summon spirits that augment your party with the haunted fox, Iris!

name: Football Manager Touch 2016
summary: Football Manager Touch 2016 is a streamlined football management simulation designed for faster play on tablets and computers. It features over 130 real leagues, cross-save compatibility between devices, and the series’ 3D match engine. New additions include Create-a-Club mode, Prozone match analysis, expanded tactical options, and various unlockables, offering a more accessible alternative to the full Football Manager experience.

name: Street Vendor Simulator
summary: Buy, sell, and earn big on the city streets by selling water.

name: Doki Doki Anomaly
summary: A weird dating-sim where you can fall in love with the monsters from SCP lore. SCP-8008-1 IS A COGNITOHAZARDOUS DATING SIM. Do not run this software without Class-4 Authorization. If you do not know why you are seeing this warning alert your local authorities IMMEDIATELY.
storyline:
Become an SCP Foundation researcher studying SCP-8008, a pair of glasses that lets you fall in love with literally anything!

Try to retain your sanity and survive your encounter with SCP-173 in the prelude to the full game.

---PERFORM EXPERIMENTS ON LIVE SCP SUBJECTS---
SCP-8008: THE NOVELTY GLASSES - A COGNITOHAZARDOUS PIECE OF EYEWEAR THAT ALLOWS THE USER TO FALL IN LOVE WITH LITERALLY ANYTHING.
BECAUSE OF YOUR COGNITIVE RESISTANCE VALUE YOU HAVE RECEIVED CLASS-5 AUTHORIZATION TO TEST THEM ON SCP-173.

[[Talk to 3 different SCP girls in intense visual novel-style dialogue sections. Make decisions that will impact the course of the story.]]

---BEWARE THE HALLUCENTATIONS---
OF THE ORIGINAL FOUR RESEARCHERS YOU ARE THE ONLY SURVIVOR. THE OTHERS WERE KILLED BY AN H2 PENCIL, A DIAMOND NECKLACE, AND A POOL NOODLE RESPECTIVELY.

[[Resist the voices in your head as you play Match-3 games in your dreams. Remember, if you don't get a high enough score, you may never wake up.]]

---YOUR CHOICES DETERMINE YOUR FATE---
THE DECISIONS YOU MAKE IN YOUR CONSCIOUS AND SUBCONSCIOUS HOURS DETERMINE THE BRANCH YOUR STORY TAKES.

[[Choose dialogue options and pick how to play the Match-3 sections to change the outcome of the story.]]

name: Impossible Stunts
summary: Prepare for an adrenaline-pumping experience in this racing game of Impossible Stunts!

name: Deadly Rain
summary: Deadly Rain is a survival horror FPS game that puts you in a terrifying fight for survival against hordes of scary mutants in a rainy, abandoned village. Find and manage resources to stay alive in the worst and most unexpected situations.
storyline: The year was 1954, the Soviet totalitarian regime needed a weapon capable of distorting reality and spreading fear and panic to non-state supporters, it was then that the Fear project began. Years later, nuclear power plants were built to infect the skies and spread the hallucinogenic material through the rain, now all that's left is for you to try to survive hell...

name: Narvas
summary: Take control of Mace in this local co-op side scrolling platform shooter as you travel from assignment to assignment taking on enemy bots and dangerous bosses on different planets.

name: Trianga's Project: Battle Splash 2.0
summary: Trianga's Project: Battle Splash 2.0 is a Friendly, Competitive, Team-based Third-Person Shooter inspired from Fast Paced Arena Shooter and modern Class Based Shooter. Using only Water as the main mechanic, Blast away your opponents in various colorful worlds that everyone can enjoy!

name: Maid for Loving You
summary: Average guy Yuuma suddenly finds his boring life becoming way more exciting when he encounters a mysterious woman named Eve. Join him as he discovers the joys of having a live-in maid in this heartwarming visual novel.
storyline:
Yuuma Kitami is your typical wage slave. Wake, work, sleep, repeat. Robbed of his ambitions by the grind, his daily life is filled with endless overtime, leaving him little time for a social life, let alone a girlfriend. But that all changes one mid-winter night. After catching the last train home, he finds a woman unconscious by his front door, mere moments from freezing to death.

Yuuma acts fast, bringing the woman into his home and doing everything in his power to warm her back to life. When she eventually comes to, the woman introduces herself as Eve and wants to thank him for saving her. To Yuuma's shock, she offers to be his maid! Though initially reluctant, he soon relents, and the two start living together.

Eve is a peculiar yet lovely woman with the odd quirk or two, and Yuuma finds himself strangely drawn to her. Join them on their journey as they learn more about each other, themselves, and the true meaning of love in Maid for Loving You!

name: Dance Break Dance
summary: In Dance Break Dance, it's all about quick reflexes and perfect timing. Spin the crank to make your adorable dancer bust out wild moves, but be sure to stop in time! The faster you crank, the crazier the dance, and the more points you score. Can you keep up with the rhythm and become the cutest dance master?

name: Angkor: Beginnings
summary: Angkor: Beginnings is a highly re-playable fantasy Match 3 with modern design and aesthetics. The game tells the story of a family trapped on an island with an active volcano. The game also includes mini games and puzzles for variety and extra fun!

name: Prison Escape Simulator: Dig Out
summary: Too long in this prison, time to get out of here. Pull the carpet and start digging with a teaspoon. Watch out for the guard, sell him the junk you find. Trade toilet paper with the prisoners. Get better items and improve your stats. Expand the tunnel, use glow sticks and dynamite. Will you escape?

name: Avariavs
summary:
In Avariavs, players choose a party of 3 heroes to battle against an opponent’s party. During battle, opposing players choose their actions simultaneously and then witness the mayhem of their decisions. Combat rages on until one winner reigns victorious by decimating their opponent’s HP to zero.

Be warned however, matches that do not conclude promptly may be subject to judgement…
storyline:
On AVARIA, emotions are dangerous. For the Hume, feeling the wrong emotion might cause an explosion or start a pandemic. For the Eoni, feeling any emotion at all could strip you of your immortality. It’s in this world that a plot is brewing among the Hume: a plot that, if fulfilled, will leave only one race standing. Kasper and his friends must dive into a world of technology, magery, politics, and ethical ambiguity to stop an almost unspeakable horror: the world’s first genocide.
World

AVARIA is home to two intelligent species. The first were the Eoni: immortal, intellectual, and entirely incapable of feeling emotion. It was only a few thousand years ago that an Eoni finally stumbled upon an emotion and, in so doing, transformed themselves into the first Hume. The Hume – beautiful, sexual, magical creatures – have been willing to live under the rule of the Eoni ever since, following their laws in exchange for guidance… until now.

name: Super Pet Hero
summary:
Take the control of the Ninja or one of his friends and save all the cute pets from dangerous crossroads. Join our crew of rescue heroes and take the pets to safety. Gather coins from the busy crossroad and on top of running cars to unlock all the pet rescue heroes.
The Ninja and his friends have a tough mission, to rescue fuzzy and cute animals from a busy crossroad. Cats, dogs, pandas and even pigs and unicorns await you! Climb the leaderboards and achieve a high score in this action packed pet rescue adventure.

name: VolticPistol
summary: Take control of the Tholos, a renounced knight on his quest to overthrow his former kingdom! Battle your way to the top of the kingdom in this action-filled medieval-cyberpunk adventure!

name: The Escape: Together
summary: The Escape: Together is a 1-3 player Online CO-OP escape horror. The paranormal creature has taken over the house. You must use everything you find to survive and make your runaway.

name: Off Road Stars
summary: Race tiny trucks around the circuit. Take control of one of up to 8 off-road racing cars and compete in a race track looking down from an isometric perspective.

name: Anonymous ME
summary: Anonymous Me is a 2D action platformer set in Qin Dynasty of China. Female assassin Meng Nv calls it quits after the organization she is in falls apart. Somehow she is plunged into a huge conspiracy. Players take the role of “Mang” and travels across China in Qin Dynasty and eliminate different enemies using cool combos, ultimately unraveling the mystery of this prosperous empire.

name: Real Farm
summary: Grow your way to success in Real Farm Sim, the most immersive agricultural sim around. Explore the 4K countryside and make it yours. Start from nothing or take on a working farm. Manage the land, crops, animals and staff, and reap the riches you sow.

name: Five Nights at Freddy's: Original Series
summary:
Explore the history of the Freddy's world famous pizzeria in this bundle containing the original 4 titles.

As always, Fazbear Entertainment is not responsible for death or dismemberment.

name: DWK 5: Hinter dem Horizont
summary:
DWK 5: Hinter dem Horizont is a traditional point & click adventure game based on the movie Die wilden Kerle 5: Hinter dem Horizont. The young soccer players Leon, Vanessa, Maxi and Raban are practising in the woods - but suddenly Leon disappears. Of course his friends search for him and suddenly arrive in the land of vampires...

The player alternately takes the control of the four protagonists and solves item based puzzles. To do so he explores his surroundings, takes everything he finds, talks with people and combines items with each other. In each scene the player can instantly switch between day and night which alters the persons he meet and the items he can interact with. When stuck the player has access to a hint system.

name: Coastline to Atmosphere
summary:
Coastline to Atmosphere is a big Single Player Modification for Half-Life 2. It's actually 15 Single Player maps with a story that links them together.

Leon Stephan Brinkmann took about 1 year to create this. He's done an excelent job to create this. With new models, such as a Keycard model, Tree models, a new shiny metal texture. And new sounds from the games Medal of Honor, Call of Duty, Soldier of Fortune 2, Max Payne 2, Cold Winter and a whole lot of ambient sounds.
storyline:
This mod continues the story where Half-Life 2 finished and offers one possible scenario. After the big explosion, you fall to the ground and are very badly injured. Some people find you and take you home to a small village outside the city where the citadel was built. After 3 months you’re strong again and want to fight on.

You have never seen Alyx or any of the others since the explosion. But you try to find new people that will fight with you against Breen. Nobody wants to help, some are afraid, others think that Breen has learned his lesson and won’t start again. It also seems that most of his organization was lost in the explosion. Then you hear that along the coast Breen is starting again and trying to take control again. So you decide to go to the coast. There you take a little boat and go along the coast so the Combine won’t notice you coming.

name: Skyblocker
summary: Skyblocker is a 3D puzzle game in which players build towers from toy blocks and try to set a global high score while battling wind and weather. It also features a "zen" mode with no scoring or time constraints, so the player can build, relax, and enjoy multiple different picturesque locales.

name: Sonic Uprising
summary: SONIC UPRISING is a 2D side-scrolling platform fan project led by bennascar and Team Giga-Drive. Uprising is inspired by the classic formula from the Mega Drive Era of Sonic the Hedgehog, expanding it by taking elements from various other titles in the series. The project's goal is to create a story inspired by SEGA's Sonic Forces, while also being able to tell a narrative that goes far beyond a simple reboot.

name: Astral Dodge
summary: A simple arcade space shooter with some upgrades, abilities, and a leader board.

name: DmC: Devil May Cry - Definitive Edition
summary: DmC: Devil May Cry - Definitive Edition includes all the stylish action gameplay from the original release, all previously released downloadable content, including the Vergil's Downfall campaign plus brand new modes and additional content, making this the ultimate offering for Devil May Cry fans. Maximizing the potential of next-gen hardware, the game's high quality production values will run at a stunning 1080p and smooth 60 fps across PlayStation 4 and Xbox One.

name: Destined
summary: Destined is a free-to-play cartoon first person shooter. Fight for victory!

name: Help me please
summary: You can't negotiate with zombies, you can't bribe or promise something in return, they will slowly but surely follow you wherever you go to destroy you. It's impossible to hide from zombies, they always sense where you're hiding. The only way to escape is to destroy them first.

name: Zugnaex
summary: Immerse yourself in Zugnaex. Compatible with DOOM and DOOM II, it blends classic FPS action with a modern user interface and a detailed heads-up display. Enjoy single-player campaigns and free* online multiplayer for epic battles. (* - requires DOOM)
storyline:
In ancient times, a powerful demon, known only by the forbidden name Zugnaex, was imprisoned by forgotten gods to prevent the destruction of reality itself. The prison, an interdimensional cage bound by immortal blood, is impenetrable, indestructible... and smells really bad. However, the gods did not realize there is one way the demon can escape. If any mortal speaks its name perfectly, every single little tiny syllable, the demon will tear through dimensions, bypass its eternal prison, and return to annihilate humankind. It’s game over and humanity is out of quarters. But Zugnaex has never faced a foe like you. Only you and your friends can defeat the demon Zugnaex and save humanity.

It’s global warfare on an epic scale to save the human race. Will you join us?

name: Crazy Chicken: Invasion
summary:
A whole armada of technically advanced alien chickens attacks with their UFOs and beams everything away that does not find shelter fast enough.

Let them come, you are prepared. Many traps and extras help you to repel the invaders before they abduct everything and everybody.

A new war of the worlds unfolds, make no mistake about it: The world is too small for two kinds of crazy chickens. Only the most talented hunters are a match for the extraterrestrial invaders.

Prevent the aliens from building a base on earth and let no one escape to call for reinforcements.

This game offers fun graphics, many hidden puzzles and extras, chickens behind every corner and enough lead to punch holes into everything.

name: Slime Musume ha Ningen to Tomodachi ni Naritai you da
summary: “Hello, humans! Will you be my friend?” This is a point-and-click novel game about Aura, a slime girl who wants to become friends with humans. Aura is pure and innocent, and easily influenced by the emotions of the humans she meets...

name: Steel Sword Story
summary: This is a game created especially for all the old school, classic 2D action game fans out there. From 8bits Fanatics, the creator of the fatally difficult action title 1001 Spikes, comes a true 2D dark fantasy-action game full of swords and magic.

name: World In Danger
summary: World In Danger is a top-down action game with stealth elements, similar to classics such as "Metal Gear". Embark on missions across the globe, taking out groups of enemies, rescuing hostages, disarming bombs and more. Face the unique and challenging boss fights the player encounters as the story unravels in this over the top action extravaganza.
storyline:
The world has become an increasingly dangerous place, the number of criminals, terrorists and general evildoers is at an all-time high. To counter this evil, decorated S.W.A.T. officer J.J. Colt founds the World Army. Together with his longtime friend Nathan "Rocket" Nace, an explosives expert and mechanical engineer. 
It is an army with no political or national allegiance, its only goal is making the world a better place by fighting evildoers on a global scale. Colt and Rocket are quickly joined by Samantha Byington, a renown competitive martial artist; and Marco Tundo, a highly trained ninja with a mysterious past. Several dozen recruits from all over the world also sign up. Some experienced or formerly retired soldier or mercenaries, others regular people with no combat experience. All of them in need of training or a refresher course before they are ready for action. 
 
The heroes are dutifully making progress towards achieving their goal. Little do they know that behind the scenes, a great evil is plotting a scheme of grand proportions...

name: Doom
summary: Doom for the Saturn is a port of the PlayStation port of Doom (which has content from Ultimate Doom and Doom II), but uses the same engine as the 32X port.

name: Trauma Record
summary: 夜を歩く、血だまりの上を走る、永遠を断ち切る。 復讐のための翼は折れない。

name: Doofas
summary:
Doofas the Dinosaur has ruled over Dinostria in great success after having opened the spazicore. The spazicore was a one way portal into the realm of Lord Grok, who was in charge of making sure universes got their fair share of evil. Doofas created the spazicore so Dinostria could toss it right back into Lord Grok's face. Grok, after having grown tired of this, decided to take matters into his own hands. Grok created Miaton and Prochun out of all his remaining evil for his attack on Dinostria... to destroy it.

The first ever game made by Scott Cawthon, known for creating 'Five Nights at Freddy's'. It was made on the game making software "Klik and Play" (now known as Clickteam Fusion) in 1994.
storyline: Doofas the Dinosaur has ruled over Dinostria for many years in great success after having opened the spazicore. The spazicore was a one way portal into the realm of Lord Grok, who was in charge of making sure that all universes got their fair share of evil, Doofas created the spazicore so Dinostria could toss it right back in Lord Groks face. Grok, after having grown tired of this, decided to take matters into his own hands. Grok created Miaton and Prochun out of all his remaining evil for him attack on Dinostria... to destroy it!

name: You Understand Kawaii
summary: Communicate with strangers' dogs.

name: Slender: Reborn
summary: Rediscover terror in this reimagined classic survival horror. Collect eight pages and evade the relentless Slenderman in a hauntingly realistic world rebuilt with updated graphics, adaptive AI, and immersive sound design. Prepare for unpredictable scares and a chilling atmosphere that redefines fear

name: Emiline: The Ghost of White Willow
summary: A psychological horror VR game. Taking place during the events of D-day, find yourself trapped in the gothic horrors of White Willow Manor Hall. Follow your sections lieutenant into combat before fighting a new battle of survival in the dark haunted past of the house.
storyline: A Gothic Horror set during the events of D-Day 1944. A British Parachute regiment finds themselves held up in a medieval manor house on the coastline of Jersey. Alfred Stuart gets left behind to look after an injured comrade when things start to take a dark turn; the manor house begins to unleash its hate onto its new victim.

name: Evil Forest
summary: A meteorite fell from sky and turned everything in the Kingdom evil. As the last hero it's your mission to destroy all the devilish creatures. Enter the portal to a fantastic world full of magic, treasures and weapons. Battle monsters, collect treasures and unravel the mystery of the ancient forest.

name: Ghostbusters: Rise of the Ghost Lord
summary: Strap on your proton pack and Meta Quest 2 and step into the world of Ghostbusters in immersive virtual reality. Run your Ghostbusters HQ in a new city, San Francisco, and unravel a rich mystery in a new chapter for the Ghostbusters universe.

name: Tumblebugs
summary:
Tumblebugs is a casual game of the match-3 genre. Players are required to shoot different coloured balls into a existing queue to make groups of three or more of the same colour, scoring points for larger groups and activating powerups.

The game takes place across over 30 distinct backgrounds and over 70 different levels which are divided into 12 stages and 5-8 rounds per stage.

The story is based around the hero, Tumble, who is saving her tumblebug friends from the evil Black Bug Empire. Tumble is the mechanism by which the player shoots the balls to make matches.

name: Super Space Pug
summary: Super Space Pug is a classic arcade shmup. Take control of 'Demetrius the Third'(Space Pug) to defend your personal space from the evil, fish flinging cats and random rocks because its a space shmup, and without rocks it would be rather non-space-y.

name: Flight of the Athena
summary:
Flight of the Athena is a unique vertical shooter, with a procedurally generated campaign and scenarios. Earn new craft, weapons and upgrades as you fly deep into enemy territory to destroy their central command, and turn the tide of this war. 
 
Get it done, Commander!

name: The Granstream Saga
summary: The Granstream Saga is an action game with strong RPG elements, and a spiritual successor to Gaia games. The player controls Eon as he explores overworld and dungeon locations, which are presented in overhead-viewed 3D. Battles are one-on-one; whenever an enemy is encountered, the view is zoomed on the combat participants who must fight each other until one of them emerges victorious. Eon can use swords, daggers, or axes against his enemies. He has a variety of attack moves at his disposal, including combos, shield-breaking abilities, etc.; he can also actively guard and cast magic spells. Leveling up, which increases Eon's attributes, occurs at set intervals throughout the game rather than from accumulating experience points.
storyline: Many years ago, the Allied Spirit Army fought the malevolent Imperial Wizardry in a prolonged war. Neither side could gain the upper hand until the Imperial Wizardry designed a weapon with too much destructive power. Causing the planet's axis to shift, the deployment of the weapon resulted in the melting of polar ice, which led to a world-wide flood. Four wise men designed a mechanism that allowed the planet's four continents to float above the water. For generations, the secrets of maintaining the mechanism have been passed from the wise men to their descendants. But now, the last of those are gone, and the planet begins to sink into the vast ocean.

name: Another Way of Gettin' Paid
summary: Juggling being a sugar baby and sugar daddy at the same time... and it only gets more complex from there!
storyline:
Ever since his college days, Shunji Naruse has been in a relationship with the female president of a real estate company, Mizuru Kozuki—as her sugar baby. Even now as a working adult, he works as her private secretary.

One day, Shunji's deliciously gratifying life gets even better when he encounters a uniformed girl, Chisato Hinata—and becomes her sugar daddy.

What's more, Shunji's sugar baby/daddy life suddenly becomes even livelier when a divorced wife and one of Mizuru's old classmates, Kasumi Tachibana; as well as Chisato's friend, Hasumi Tachibana—get added to the mix.

As his various partners begin to interact in ways they were never supposed to, Shunji finds his circle of lovers expanding farther than he could have ever imagined...

name: Super Hipster Lumberjack
summary: You can't beat this game!!! Noah attempts to make a game for the first time. He then gets trapped in his own creation.

name: Truck Simulator US Driver
summary:
Step into the shoes of a true TRUCK SIMULATOR US DRIVER, a captivating game that takes you across the endless highways of the United States. Whether you're passionate about trucks or simply looking for a realistic driving experience, this simulator offers the chance to explore major cities, deliver various cargo, and live the life on the open road.

TRUCK SIMULATOR US DRIVER is more than just a game – it’s a virtual journey through the heart of America, filled with challenges, strategic decisions, and relaxing moments on the road. Whether you're a simulation fan or just seeking a unique adventure, this title offers an authentic and engaging experience. Start your engine and conquer the roads of the United States!

name: Scarlett's Dungeon
summary: "Scarlett's Dungeon" consists of an action rpg zelda-like game with 2D pixel art graphics, top-down view & randomly generated dungeons! ^^

name: Kingdomino
summary: Kingdomino is a cosy 1-4 player tile-laying strategy game of kingdom building. Place colorful dominoes, match terrains, and crown your lands to create the most prosperous realm. Simple to learn yet deeply strategic game perfect for quick sessions, solo challenges, or competitive multiplayer.

name: Cryonauts
summary: MMO action Sci-fi game set in the future year of 2069 where you play as a cybernetic robot to eliminate other robots that represent Biomorph defence system, gameplay take place in Egypt near an ancient temple complex along the Nile river.
storyline:
Biomorphx a famous company working in genetics and medical development began "Cryonauts" project a unauthorized mass cloning of human infants, all forms of human cloning is prohibited by the UN worldwide, Cryonauts have to be terminated at all cost, the battle is inevitable.

Year 2069 You play as a cybernetic robot that was hacked and dispatched from control network that represent Biomorphx defence system to counter attack their original hostile Cybernetic robots that protect it to terminate unauthorized human cloning activities at one of its production facilities located in Egypt near an ancient temple complex along the Nile river.

name: Puniru ha Kawaii Slime no Game wo "Ano Game" de Tsukuttemita Keredo, Hatashite Anata ha Clear Dekirunoka?
summary: This game is a collection of three mini-games with 150 stages, created by D3 Publisher in collaboration with Dokokade Mita “Ano Ga ”me Tachi wo Bouningen de Tsukuttemita Keredo.

name: Old Coin Pusher Friends
summary: This is an online cooperative coin pusher game set in the Old japan that can be enjoyed by one or all. Cooperate with other players and aim for the jackpot. In addition, by collecting prizes, new content is released and coins are easily increased. Online multiplayer for up to five players possible.
storyline:
Online Multi Play
There are random matching and friend matching where you can play only with your friends. With random matching, you can enjoy a once-in-a-lifetime experience; with friend matching, you can have fun in private; and of course, you can play solo, so you can enjoy the game in your preferred play style.

Co-op event
There is a demon extermination event where you have to kill demons, and a jar game where you have to put coins into a jar like a ball game. It looks easy, but it is quite difficult, but don't be afraid. Don't be afraid, because you can cooperate with other players. However, it's not impossible to clear solo.

name: Zombie Tactics
summary: Tactical turn-based zombie survival game, featuring full story, survival mode, and alternative endings! Lead your team through the zombie apocalypse, earning items and skill points along the way. What ethical choices will you make later in the story?

name: Project Tal
summary: An open-world action Korean mythology RPG. Players will explore a detailed and in-depth world across a single-player adventure inspired by ancient folklore that reimagines Korea’s traditional Tal masks. Engage with an array of threats from massive monsters to formidable swordsmen, making use of enemy weak points, counterattacks, unique abilities, and more.

name: Serpico
summary: Serpico is a first-person hack and slash fantasy game set on a mysterious island filled with ancient ruins, divine powers, and lurking darkness.

name: Cozy Space Survivors
summary: A cozy time survival roguelite in space. You steer the shippy while the shooting happens automatically. Meet cute NPCs, solve small quests, and fight quirky enemies with satisfying weapons. A short experience for people who don't have much time but love playing (and finishing) games.

name: Cyber Ops
summary: Become a military hacker and help your black ops team reach their goal in this noir cyberpunk tactical game. Scan, hack, overtake, control and manage high tech devices, vehicles and even enemy cyborgs with cutting-edge implants.
storyline:
The young nation of Baltia has earned its right to freedom after a long and painful war, but now the stakes are higher than ever before.

You are part of the Geist Division, a secret high-tech unit created by the government to protect the country from all kinds of next-gen threats. As the Operator, your mission is to provide remote support to a group of spec-ops agents deployed in urban terrains. You must control devices and systems with your deep hacking abilities, and scan the environment to provide the safest routes for your squad.

name: Midnight Scenes: The Nanny
summary: The Nanny is a short interactive horror story about the supernatural. Follow siblings Oliver and Tina in their quest to find their nanny after she disappears in the middle of the night. Welcome to a new dimension of horror. Welcome to Midnight Scenes.

name: Dragon Bobby: The Story of a Life
summary: A uniquely beautiful game with third-person exploration and puzzles that tells the story of a man's life from birth. You control a dragon who is an analogy of this man in the story. A true reflection on life.

name: The Pool Invasion
summary: Use your arrow keys to balance the tower from the first level and for the other levels. Zack and Cody are at the pool and because they got bored they decided to play some funny games that will also get them points. Help Zack and Cody get through every level of the game without their mother seeing them and without getting punished.

name: DCS World: Iraq Map
summary: Experience the full scope of Iraq's diverse and historically rich environment with DCS: Iraq. Fly over the entire country, from the deserts of the south to the mountains of the north, and immerse yourself in a landscape that has been the backdrop for some of the most significant air campaigns in history.

name: Belle Boomerang
summary:
Face off against an army of ever-changing foes and turn their own powers against them in Belle Boomerang!
Play as Belle, the destined heroine, and master her legendary boomerang! Through the effects of a mysterious spell, the beloved monarchs have been transformed into hostile beasts! Defeat them in battle, lift their curse, and infiltrate the corrupted tower to raise the curtain on this evil scheme! But no boomerang alone can save this kingdom... Belle Boomerang will be tossing cherries, soaring through flame-filled skies, possessing ancient statues, and more!

name: Parsec
summary:
Parsec is a computer game for the Texas Instruments TI-99/4A. Perhaps the best-remembered of all TI-99/4A games, it is a side-scrolling shooter, programmed in 1982 by Jim Dramis (who also programmed the popular TI-99/4A games Car Wars and Munch Man) and Paul Urbanus.

The player in Parsec pilots a spaceship through sixteen differently-colored levels of play which scroll horizontally over the screen. The objective is to avoid being shot by an enemy ship, colliding with any flying object and/or the ground, and destroy all enemy ships without overheating one's laser cannon.

Three waves of fighters attack, alternating with three waves of cruisers. Enemy ships enter the screen one at a time. A ship flying off the left edge of the screen wraps around to the right side and attacks again. A new fighter can appear with others still on the screen, whereas a new cruiser will not come until the previous one is destroyed. The fighters pose only the threat of collision, while the cruisers fire on the player's ship. The fighter types are named Swoopers, LTFs (Light Triangular Fighters), and Saucers. The cruisers are called Urbites, Dramites, and Bynites. Each level ends with an asteroid belt, in which an array of asteroids advance on the ship and must be avoided or shot. At the end of each asteroid belt, any remaining asteroids are cleared away and the color of the ground is changed, then a new wave of Swoopers begins. Starting with level 4, the Swoopers are preceded by a random number of Killer Satellites, which come without the usual computer warning.

The Urbites and Dramites appear to be named after the developers of the game, while the Bynites were apparently named after Don Bynum (the manager of TI's Personal Computer Division) or possibly named after the fact that they have invisibility (by night). In fact, Paul Urbanus signed Internet posts as late as 2005 as "urbite".

name: Train Sim World 3: Amtrak's Acela
summary: America's Fastest Train! Race along Northeast Corridor rails in iconic style, reaching incredible speeds through multiple states and suburbs. “Train approaching, please remain behind yellow line”, Amtrak's Acela blasts into Train Sim World 3!

name: DCS World: Flaming Cliffs 3
summary: DCS World: Flaming Cliffs 3 is the next evolution of the Flaming Cliffs series that operates with DCS World. FC3 features the F-15C, A-10A, Su-27, Su-33, MiG-29A, MiG-29S and Su-25. The FC3 aircraft provide an easy learning curve for new players and focuses on a broad range of aircraft rather than a detailed single aircraft.

name: AneeMate
summary:
AneeMate is a PvPvE creature extraction shooter where survival means more than just staying alive—you must rescue, evolve, and fight for the future of the AneeMates. Built in Unreal Engine 5, this high-intensity adventure blends exploration, combat, and AI-driven strategy, creating a dynamic and unpredictable battleground.

Explore, Catch, Level Up—Decide the Fate of AneeMates

name: Midio!
summary: MiDiO! is a cozy decoration game, creature collector and platformer! Build and share your own DIO room or view and explore others! Connect with Twitch and let your audience collect cute little critters you can interact with!

name: Mad Bullets
summary: Mad Bullets, the wackiest shooter is here to put your reflexes and laughing muscles to an intensive test. You can forget about boring stories, complicated controls and irritating tutorials, and jump right into a mind blowing, high-speed action. Now is the time to become the hero of the Wild West and shoot your way up to the top of the leaderboards! Do you think you have what it takes to face a real challenge?

name: I did it Mum! Spelling
summary: An educational touch-screen game which aims to teach children how to spell.

name: Ascendshaft and Endless Shaft
summary:
2 games in one Ascendshaft and Endless Shaft

Ascendshaft:
While exploring deep underground caves on an alien planet, worldwide seismic activity triggers a cave in which leaves only one narrow channel of ascent

A tale of action, horror, romance.... and betrayal

Endless Shaft:
Take control of the Perpetually Descending Man as he plummets ever downwards in five never ending shafts, each providing a unique challenge.

Avoid bats, rocks, missiles and more.

Compete to achieve the highest score on the online leaderboards (android version only).

Procedurally generated levels.

Special boulder throw and dive abilities add more nuance to the gameplay than you would expect.

Fearsome boss level to be unlocked.

name: Alive 2 Survive
summary: Zombie hordes. Hostile humans. Fight to survive! Swipe your way through life or death decisions where each choice can be the difference between surviving the apocalypse or joining the zombie horde. A swipe-to-survive zombie apocalypse decision making adventure.

name: Mutant Kingdom
summary: Mutant Kingdom thrusts you into a haunting, ever-changing world where survival hinges on clever deckbuilding and tactical exploration. Harness the power of dynamic weather and elemental synergies, discover game-changing items, and unleash adrenaline-pumping combos.

name: Final Sword: Definitive Edition
summary: The source of evil, it has brought numerous monster corps. Defeat the source of evil by acquiring various skills and magics through the adventure. You will experience breathtaking battles with real fantasy monsters.

name: Verdure
summary: Shape nature your way in a surreal playground of infinite plants and trees. Tweak their recipes, prune or let them flourish, and save your best creations into an ever growing collection.

name: Wild West Survival
summary: Wild West Survival is an open world sandbox game where you survive by crafting, building, hunting, farming, fishing, and mining.

name: Lab
summary: Explore and escape a mutant infested lab. Collect weapons, health and armor upgrades and fight and try to survive the onslaught!

name: Department of Collections
summary: A tasked based procedural online co-op sci-fi horror game that can be played both casually or more hardcore

name: SuperLite 1500 Series: Sudoku 4
summary:
Sudoku is a logic-based, combinatorial number-placement puzzle. The objective is to fill a 9×9 grid with digits so that each column, each row, and each of the nine 3×3 sub-grids that compose the grid (also called "boxes", "blocks", "regions", or "sub-squares") contains all of the digits from 1 to 9. The puzzle setter provides a partially completed grid, which typically has a unique solution.

Completed puzzles are always a type of Latin square with an additional constraint on the contents of individual regions. For example, the same single integer may not appear twice in the same 9x9 playing board row or column or in any of the nine 3x3 subregions of the 9x9 playing board.

The puzzle was popularized in 1986 by the Japanese puzzle company Nikoli, under the name Sudoku, meaning single number. It became an international hit in 2005.

SuperLite 1500 Series - Suudoku 4 is the fourth sudoku game in the series for the Playstation One console that features over 198 different sudoku challenges. The game features 3 different difficulty levels (easy, medium & hard) each of them with several sudoku puzzles..

name: Canasta 3D Premium
summary: Realistic 3D Canasta simulation with singleplayer, multiplayer and tutorial. With configurable AI strength and many adjustable rule and game variants you can start exciting Canasta tournaments - or just play for fun!

name: Gardener
summary: In Gardener, every leaf matters. Unveil the potential of the next-gen virtual garden🥕. Plant and maintain accurately simulated gardens, made of your own procedurally generated plant species. Discover, grow and shape unlimited species. Become a Gardener of Tomorrow‍.

name: Sword of the Stars: The Pit Gold Edition - Necromancer
Transformers: Mystery of Comvoy
summary:
Transformers: Comvoy no Nazo is a 2D side-scrolling action platformer developed by ISCO and published by TAKARA for the Nintendo Entertainment System (in Japan only) on Decmber 5, 1986. Set in the first-generation Transformers universe, players control Autobot Ultra Magnus as he storms through various Decepticon strongholds to find the whereabouts of Autobot leader Convoy (known worldwide as Optimus Prime).

Convoy no Nazo consists of nine stages, each ending in a boss battle. Players can move and shoot as well as transform into a more maneuverable vehicle mode. The game is so difficult, most players do not usually pass the first stage. The 9th stage is a maze which, if not completed in precisely the right way, will infinitely loop. Warp Zones can be found by locating Bumblebee in some levels.

name: Dead by Headshot
summary: A first-person survival shooter with apocalyptic simulation elements, focused on precision and headshot mechanics. Every shadow hides a deadly threat. Survive the night, manage your ammo, and fight off ever-increasing waves. Do you have what it takes to resist?

name: Operation DogFight
summary: Take to the skies in a world of conflict between humankind's best friends and the evil cat empire! Experience over-the-top flight combat in a thrilling Story Mode that’ll leave your tail wagging, or fetch up to three of your bestest friends and compete to find the top-dog in local multiplayer.
storyline: Take to the skies in a world of conflict between humankind's best friends in Operation DogFight! Fetch up to three of your bestest friends to compete and see who the top-dog is in frantic local multiplayer action. Operation DogFight is best played with controllers, but can support up to one person on Keyboard/Mouse.

name: FarmingCat
summary: You're a cat in a world of islands. You can explore, craft, cook, build, destroy, collect drops and discover items of old ancestors. Don't worry about monsters, no one will attack you. But you have to care about food, stamina and economy!

name: Jungle Jinx
summary: Set up camp deep in the jungle and begin your adventure! Explore lost ruins, collect artifacts, upgrade your gear, and grow your expedition. In Jungle Jinx, choose your path: dodge deadly traps, fight enemies, or race through the jungle on wild karts!

name: Vampire Savior: The Lord of Vampire
summary: This is the 3rd in the Darkstalkers series. It plays much the same as the first, but features better animation, more playable characters, and a deeper storyline.
storyline: Jedah, one of the high nobles of Makai, is resurrected after a premature death long ago. Seeing the state of the demon world, he decides that the only way to save the world is to recreate it. To this end, he conjures a dimension known as Majigen, to which he summons worthy souls to feed his new world. As luck would have it, those souls belong to the characters from the first two games, in addition to three newcomers.

name: Apocalypse
summary: Apocalypse is a multi-user dungeon (MUD) built on a codebase called DIKU. The code has been modified over the course of about twenty-six years to come into its current state. Apocalypse draws heavily upon the world of Athas and the lore of Dark Sun.

name: Skedaddling In Egypt
summary: Skedaddling In Egypt is a first person speedrunning game where you use your parkour skills and mummy wrappings to swing and slide your way through your crumbling tomb. Compete with others through an online leaderboard, collect treasures, and more!

name: Rinth
summary:
Rinth is an old school dungeon rpg with 90s style.

Enter the dungeons and face different monsters and bosses.

Collect weapons, buy/sell and craft them to get even better ones.

name: Your Cattle
summary: An interactive casual game. By utilizing mechanics such as charging, knocking back, stunning, and blink, players can hone their skills in a low-pressure environment.Accompanied by exquisite music and smooth interactions, relieve emotional stress.

name: Now You See

Uncover horrible secrets within as you use your wits and the items you find to escape this immersive blood soaked nightmare.

name: Estab Life: Unity Memories
summary:
Estab Life: Unity Memories is a multiplayer action role-playing video game developed and published by Square Enix that was announced in 2022 as part of a multimedia promotion of the Estab Life manga.

As of March 2024, this game has not been released yet.
storyline:
The world’s population has peaked and begun to shrink. Humanity has developed artificial intelligence that manages the ecosystem and carried out “Humanity Diversification Experiments” for the prosperity of its kind. Diverse races—such as humans, beastmen, and demons created by genetic manipulation—have created diverse cities known as “clusters,” protected by walls.

There are many clusters, each with their own culture and people. And to ensure they do not perish, they live under the constant supervision of artificial intelligence.

summary: There is a classic porn story. Steven works as plumber in Springfield. You think it's dirty job? Yeah! But he loves it. Every day he has a chance to meet with another sexy housewife.

name: The Lost Battalion

The mod combines custom-made assets, detailed operations, and a structured unit system to deliver an authentic tactical experience. Developed and maintained by its own dedicated community, The Lost Battalion runs continuous story-driven campaigns and handcrafted missions that emphasize teamwork, realism, and dynamic combat scenarios.

name: Train Sim World 3: Dispolok BR 182 Add-On
summary: Dispolok delivering duties await – climb aboard the sleek and stylish EuroSprinter dressed in iconic yellow accents, ready for service on nightly fast freight trains with Train Sim World 3: Dispolok BR 182!

name: Dark Adventure
summary: Dark Adventure is a dimetric action-adventure game produced by Konami that was released for the arcades in North America in 1987.[3] It was the first arcade game by Konami that allowed up to three players simultaneously. The game was also released as Majū no Ōkoku in Japan and as Devil World in other countries outside North America, although these versions feature significant gameplay differences and only allow up to two players.
storyline: An archeologist named Dr. Condor discovers the coffin of a demon in ancient ruins. During a press conference announcing his discovery, he decides to open the coffin for the first time, only to be transported into another world alongside a reporter named Labryna and another archeologist named Zorlock. The three heroes must now fight their way out of the Devil World in order to defeat the evil Demon King who is keeping them trapped and return to the human world.

name: DCS World: AV-8B Night Attack V/STOL
summary: The AV-8B project was born in the early 1970's as an effort to address the operational inadequacies of the AV-8A first generation Harrier, aimed to dramatically improve the capabilities and performance of the early AV-8A's.

name: Vanildo's Journey
summary: Vanildo, a skilled retired adventurer is forced to return to work because of the peculiar events that are taking place in the city of Pirarotoba, including the disappearance of his old friend.

name: Parked in the Dark
summary: Find you car somewhere in the garage by finding clues, before the time runs out. But you are not as alone as you think...

name: Everlast
summary:
Thank you for choosing Everlast - where death is just a new beginning. Get ready to enter a playground full of infinite options for your digitized mind. We're honored that you've chosen to store your consciousness with us. Because you deserve an afterlife full of possibility. Your account activation will begin shortly. Restriction may apply. Afterlife membership tier eligibility is contingent on past behavior in digital spaces. Welcome!

Everlast is an FMV game in which you play as a recently-deceased person being onboarded to a new virtual existence. All the characters in the game were generated using artificial intelligence.

name: Break My Case
summary:
"I'll take care of that problem for you."

A story about unraveling and cutting tangled threads.

Aporia, a store staffed by talented but somewhat out-of-the-ordinary employees, has two faces.
After operating as an ordinary cafe, only a limited number of customers are offered a relaxing time and special services.

Anything that can be done in place of a living person>

In a city where everything is saturated, responding to what is "not enough" - multi agency.

"You should work for me! As my representative, that is...as the owner's representative!"

A strange connection with such a store.
Surpass the situation on behalf of someone else.
An uncertain and sad day begins with them, where anything can take their place.

name: Cartoon Cartoon Food Bash
summary: A Flash game formerly featured on the Cartoon Network website featuring characters from Johnny Bravo, Ed, Edd n Eddy, The Powerpuff Girls, and Samurai Jack.

name: Eggconsole Schwarzschild PC-9801
summary: Become the young king of the Sankuri Star Nation and unify all the star systems of the galaxy. Enjoy a space opera in this turn-based sci-fi simulation game.

name: My Club Dino
summary: My Club Dino is an online fun and educational dinosaur game, targeted for young kids in between 5 and 12 years old. My Club Dino combines fun, education and interaction

name: Diamond Hollow
summary: Shoot, upgrade, conquer enemies, attempt achievements, collect gems, all in an attempt to escape an endless cave

name: Marippy
summary: Marippy is a Touhou fan game based on the arcade game Mappy. The game has the player play as Marisa Kirisame as she collects items from Alice Margatroid's house which Alice had stole.

name: Eclipse Survivors
summary: Experience the ultimate challenge in Eclipse Survivors, a bullet-hell / area shooter game featuring epic bosses inspired by classic 16-bit titles. Collect XP gems, master unique skills, and dodge countless enemy bullets as you face off against hordes of foes. Will you survive the eclipse?

name: Her Name Was Fire
summary: Her Name Was Fire is a Tarotpunk twin stick roguelike with deck building elements where you progressively unlock spells and upgrades to defeat hordes of void creatures. Survive the 5 stages of grief and vanquish the Major Allegories.

name: Super Block Boy and Friends
summary: Super Block Boy and Friends is an exhilarating 2D precision platformer that puts your skills and sanity to the ultimate test. Dive into our world of challenging levels that reward grit and persistence.

name: Way of the Hunter: Hunter's Advantage Pack
summary: Enhance your hunting experience with the Hunter’s Advantage Pack, featuring three specialized rifles and a versatile electronic caller. Designed for all types of wildlife, this DLC delivers precision, power, and adaptability in every shot.

name: Ecchi Puzzle
summary: Ecchi Puzzle is a sliding puzzle game.

name: Rheum
summary: Jump down the esophagus of a body plagued by viruses and big bad bosses in this reverse vertical scrolling shoot'em up! Collect eye crusties, upgrade your pupils, and clear the screen of bullets with your cornea crushing eye blasts!
storyline:
A mass of muscle and teeth lay dormant before you. As you inch your way closer, it comes alive. A sphincter crying for help, beckons you to descend. Your only option is down. 
 
Travel through a fleshly vessel, as an eyeball, collecting rheum [eyeball crusties] to grow stronger in your fight against the infection plaguing this.......body. 
 
Upgrade your pupils, dodge bullets, and clear the screen of projectiles with cornea crushing blasts!

name: Luminleaf Chronicles
summary: "Luminleaf Chronicles" is the story of a group of cat girls who set out on an adventure to purify the world's water. In this game, you can choose different characters to go on your own adventures with others.
storyline:
"Luminleaf Chronicles" is the story of a group of cat girls who set out on an adventure to purify the world's water.
In this game, you can choose different characters and go on your own adventures with others.

Each Megastructure will have its own unique identity and gameplay, unlocking new possibilities and rewards. Harness the power of Megatech to take Basebuilding and Automation to a whole new level! This DLC will be completely compatible with existing saves, and builds off of any progress you’ve already made in game, feel free to start fresh, or load up your existing saves and start building!

name: E30 Drift Car Simulator
summary: E30 car modification options and a funny drift game are waiting for you.

name: Danmaku Unlimited 4 Wyver Ultra
summary: Arise Wyver and fly against overwhelming odds in this modern labor of love tribute to classic shoot'em ups!

name: Project Tristars
summary:
The previous activities for the 5th anniversary of the debut of the idol group "3 Majesty" "XIP" is recorded. You can enjoy their documentary from a new aspect, by choosing valuable scenes of the idols
Video of the performance of "3 Majesty × XIP LIVE - SPLASH SUMMER FES 2017" held at DMM VR THEATER in August 2017 and footage of the popular "Victory Live" at the app version "Tokimeki Restaurant" Total 15 or more recorded
All the visuals displayed in important scenes of documentaries are photographed by Makoto Maekazaki. You can see not only the idols that you always expected but also the new aspect of them such as how to strive behind the scenes
storyline: This game's scenarios continues from the live dramas in 3 Majesty×X.I.P. LIVE -SPLASH SUMMER FES 2017-. Its presentation is meant to be a live documentary, as each member recalls their group origins to a faceless and mute camera man working with the director. Unlike previous instances, Project TRISTARS provides in-depth personal insights and illustrated content for about five months of the groups' formations.

name: RimWorld: Console Edition
summary: A sci-fi colony sim driven by an intelligent AI storyteller. Generates stories by simulating psychology, ecology, gunplay, melee combat, climate, biomes, diplomacy, interpersonal relationships, art, medicine, trade, and more.

name: Coonwood
summary: Coonwood is a multiplayer horror game. One player takes on the role of the alien who crashed on an unknown planet. The other players (1-4) play as raccoons. But in the place where they are located, anomalies occur and the characters begin to possess different abilities.

name: Super Smash Bros. for Wii U: Hyrule Castle
Tsukimi Planet
summary: A boy named Utarou wakes up in his deathbed, being told that he has a short amount of time left to live. As he's letting the news sink in, a girl that's apparently an alien named Tsukimi pops up by his window and offers to grant him any wish he has. What will he wish for, and how will it turn out for him?
storyline: A boy named Utarou wakes up in his deathbed, being told that he has a short amount of time left to live. As he's letting the news sink in, a girl that's apparently an alien named Tsukimi pops up by his window and offers to grant him any wish he has. What will he wish for, and how will it turn out for him?

name: SandTest
summary: A Flash falling sand game by onimatrix, hosted on Kongregate.

name: Li Li Nuo De Qi Huan Zhi Lu
summary: Lina was judged a witch by the church, and Lilina was ordered to execute her best friend... After a few years, theia territory again appeared the trace of the devil, Lilina decided to seek the truth in those days, set foot on the journey.

name: Deflector
summary:
A puzzle game where your objective is to control a laser beam towards its destination. You goal is to redirect the laser beam from its source to the destination using objects like mirrors and prisms. But beware! There are valuable objects in the way that you must work around in order to win.

There are 90 unique levels with 3 different difficulty modes to test your puzzle skills to deflect the laser to its destination

name: Soul Edge
summary: Soul Edge is a 3D arcade fighting game and the first in the Soul series, it is one of the first 3D fighting game in history that place a particular emphasis on the story of the fighters. Each character have their own weapon, allowing for a wide range of play styles. The slower, longer ranged characters try to deliver their heavy blows from a distance whereas the quicker, faster characters try to get in as close as possible and deliver quick-hitting attacks.
storyline: In the 16th century, an extremely powerful sword named Soul Edge surfaces and attracts evil warriors from around the world who want its power. From America to Europe to Japan, these warriors fight each other for the chance to obtain it.

name: Tiger Tank 59 I: Mission Pack 063
summary: The classic tank battle game re-opens, guarding your base and defeating all enemy tanks.

name: Vice Thief Simulator: 80s Nostalgia
summary: Every street holds danger, fortune, and opportunity.

name: Toys vs. Nightmares
summary:
The nightmares have been unleashed from your closet and all you have are some books and toy soldiers….

Strategize and defend yourself from the evil monsters lurking in your closet. Use robots, rubber frogs, and miners to stop the ghosts and make it through the night.

name: Hispalis: Proyecto NoDo
summary:
Discover the free video game created by two Pokémon -loving fans from Seville that's taking Andalusia by storm.

Immerse yourself in the history of Hispalis , a post-apocalyptic Seville devastated by a massive pandemic, where Pokémon now reign supreme.

name: Mechatris
summary: Punch, smash, and stack as waves of falling blocks keep coming!

name: Marky Mark and the Funky Bunch: Make My Video
summary: Make My Video: Marky Mark and the Funky Bunch is a video game based on real-time editing of music video footage. The setup is that a brother and sister pair is arguing about what would make the best Marky Mark video. Since they can not agree, they enlist help from some other people: A boxer and his trainer, a trio of teenage girls, the members of a garage band, and their parents. Each group has their ideas about what an ideal Marky Mark video should or should not contain. The specifications normally come in the form of a set of pictures they either do or don't want to see, and perhaps some effects. The game has three Marky Mark videos from which to choose: "Good Vibrations", "I Need Money", and "You Gotta Believe".

name: The Divine Speaker: The Sun and the Moon
summary: The story-rich 18+ prequel to The Divine Speaker. Follow alongside a younger Aemyl as he uncovers the world for himself!
storyline:
Journey to the past with The Divine Speaker: The Sun and the Moon, an enthralling fantasy visual novel and 18+ prequel to the popular BL game, The Divine Speaker.​​

Follow the intertwining journeys of Lucius and Aemyl as they navigate their past and future, each grappling with the fate they have been dealt. Will they be able to find a happy future, or does only pain and suffering await them?

Lucius longs for a past that he cannot return to, while Aemyl is fixated on creating a future that may not come to pass. As their paths cross and their stories become intertwined, each must come to terms with the destiny that awaits them... or refuse to accept it.

In a game of the past and the future, the sun and the moon, who will come out on top?

name: Red Rust Pioneers
summary:
Your story begins stranded in the unforgiving wilderness of the Wild West.

Your one goal: to survive.

Endure scorching days and freezing nights as you battle hunger, thirst, and the elements. Forage for food, hunt wildlife, and fish to stay alive. Scavenge the land to gather vital resources and craft the tools and weapons you’ll need to stand a chance in this brutal but breathtaking frontier.

Can you master the elements and withstand blistering heat, violent rainstorms and freezing cold winters?

Should you beat the odds and live, alone or with up to three friends, you’ll find yourself in a gorgeous, rugged, vibrant land. Will you be able to not only survive, but thrive?

Build and grow your camp your way with easy to use base building mechanics. Fish in the lakes and rivers, or hunt in the atmospheric woodlands and open prairies. Farm and harvest a variety of crops to establish a self-sufficient camp. Adventure high into the mountains to mine resources, and craft better weapons and tools.

Explore a beautifully realized, open world, fictionalized Wild West frontier and become the first to discover the untamed wilderness of Red Rust Valley.

If you can overcome the threat of extreme hunger, brutal weather conditions and lethal wildlife you may just live to appreciate it.

name: Spirits of the Unloved
summary: You, Youtuber James Pink, go into a haunted orphanage in order to get footage for your upcoming video. You are faced with paranormal activity in the orphanage while recording your footage.

name: Princess Minerva
summary: Princess Minerva is a role-playing video game developed and published by Riverhillsoft for the NEC PC-9801 in 1992 in Japan only. An original video animation by Group TAC was originally released by Toho in May 1995 in Japan; it was later released also in the United States. The extended franchise also includes a manga series, an illustrated serial novel, and other media.
storyline: In the game, the evil sorceress Dynastar challenges Princess Minerva, threatening to kidnap all the girls in the world and turn them into monsters. Minerva leaves with her eight personal female bodyguards to defeat Dynastar and her six also female demon generals. The game starts when all their weapons, armor and money gets stolen.

name: Loretta's Brand New Job
summary: Loretta's husband Elio has started a promising new job at a newspaper. However, a politician Elio used to work with is now coercing Elio to write positive articles about him, putting Elio's reputation at risk. To protect her husband, Loretta begins to look into this man's past...

name: Dai-4-ji Super Robot Taisen
summary: Dai-4-ji Super Robot Taisen is a Sci-Fi Turn-Based Strategy game, developed and published by Banpresto, which was released in Japan in 1995.
storyline:
4 Months has passed since the Inspector Conflict, the Earth Sphere is once again in peace. But the increased number of terrorists that appeared throughout the world caused by the Divine Crusaders escalates, and put economic strains into the colonies which leads to some colonies in rebelling again the Earth Sphere. Brigander General Jamitov Hymem formed the group Titans to strengthen the army against the terrorists.

As Londo Bell returns from La Gaias after the events of EX, Bright Noah decides to leave his position for a while in search for Lieutenant Quarto Bajena, who went missing for unknown reasons. He parted with the Getter Team under the direction of John Kowen for his search and unravel some events happening in the current world. Things go to worse as Ondora Poseidal declared war on the surface world and even worse, the Divine Crusaders is revived by Neo Zeon Leader Haman Khan under the name Neue DC to take over the Earth Sphere.

With the war escalates, an unknown army from another galaxy called the Guests has arrived in the Earth Sphere led by the United Solar System Army Commander, Teniquette Zezenan. The reveal themselves to be part of the Zovorg Alliance which is where the Inspectors originated. With no options left, the Londo Bell must initiate Operation Final with their last fight against the Zovorg for the survival of their planet.

name: Ruins to Rumble
summary: Ruins to Rumble is a sandbox colony survival in a 2D side scroller environment. Build, fight, explore and defend to claim victory against other factions and monsters.

name: Approaching Infinity: Shipyards
summary: Design your own custom starting ship with a point-based system and access to every weapon and device in the game. Tow 5-deck shipwrecks to get more points. Space stations will offer more ships for sale, and the asteroid base will have a brand new ship upgrade service: the Shipwright!

name: Laser Grid
summary: Laser Grid is a first-person puzzle game in which you power devices by redirecting, combining and splitting different colored lasers. 32 mind bending puzzle rooms to master with 10+ hours of gameplay. Use a variety of different cube types such as glass, magnet, diffraction, laser, and Fresnel.

name: Far Cry 3: Blood Dragon - Classic Edition
summary: Far Cry 3 Blood Dragon Classic Edition is THE 80's-style sci-fi cyber shooter, taking place on a bizarre open world island crawling with evil - now on the current generation of consoles.
storyline:
The year is 2007 and Earth has been ravaged by a nuclear war which erupted in the 90's. The east vs. west conflict has raged for generations, and humanity continues to struggle to progress after a disastrous decade. New paths for peace must be found, and the US cyborg army may have found a solution: a powerful bio weapon on a distant island. Your mission is to gather information and figure out what the hell is going on.

As Sergeant Rex Colt, you are part man, part machine, all American. You are a state-of-the-art Mark IV cyber commando on a mission… of vengeance. You’re out to bring down your old commanding officer and his battalion of ruthless killer cyborgs-and you’ll stop at nothing to get the job done.

name: Helicopter Game
summary: A browser game about flying a helicopter down an infinite corridor. See how far you can go without crashing. Only one button is used to fly. It has been re-released for mobile devices.

name: 1112: Episode 02
summary: In 1112 Episode 02, players continue the journey with Louis Everett, who now finds himself in New York under mysterious circumstances. This sequel amplifies the intrigue as players help Louis unravel the reasons behind his unexpected arrival in the bustling city. Promising unforeseen twists and encounters, the game offers hours of engaging gameplay. This episode elevates the experience with an all-new advanced graphical design and artistic direction, featuring 25 expansive and detailed environments. Players will meet 14 new characters, each adding to the rich tapestry of the story. The game's diverse puzzles, each with unique gameplay mechanics, challenge and engage players at every turn. Complemented by an original score, this installment of 1112 maintains its elaborate interactive narrative, immersing players deeper into Louis's increasingly complex world.

name: Temple of Shadows
summary:
Embark on an epic adventure as Sabastian Harrington, a passionate archeology grad student turned explorer, in search of his missing professor. Six weeks ago, Dr. Albert J. Montgomery III announced the discovery of a hidden temple, but he never returned. Now, Sabastian must dive into ancient temple ruins, solve intricate puzzles, and uncover hidden secrets. Will you reveal the mysteries within the Temple of Shadows?

Navigate the enigmatic Temple Ruins and unlock the secrets of the Temple Gate. Venture into the labyrinthine caves beyond, a realm filled with ancient mysteries and hidden dangers. Your mission: uncover the truth and track down the elusive Dr. Montgomery. Embark on this thrilling adventure and face challenges that will test your courage and wits at every turn. Can you reveal the secrets that lie within?

name: Kollywood: The Game
summary: Kollywood: The Game is a stop motion video, comedy game with quick-time event fight scenes inspired by Tamil Cinema.

name: Christmas Cat
summary: The Bonte cat jumps on top of the Christmas tree and sends the 20 red balls all around the house. Can you find all 20 balls by solving the puzzles?

name: Justin Danger
summary: Runventure awaits! Jump in to the action and explore mysterious lands in search of treasures. Avoid the danger, run through various locations. Jungles, temples, castles and many other places loaded with deadly traps and hordes of enemies. Use your reflexes to jump over hot lava, or rope swing over piranha pools escape the deadly skeletons and hungry wolves. - Super sharp vector graphics! - Explore mysterious lands with parallax backgrounds. - Tons of characters to unlock and level up - Great levels, obstacles and enemies to beat Build the team of experienced explorers, level them up, complete challenges and unlock precious treasures. Now it’s time for adventure, it’s time for Runventure!

name: Giraffe Evolution
summary:
Long neck, camel-like shape, leopard-like coloring and horn-like ossicones don’t come out of nowhere: giraffes are naturally bizarre. What would happen if mutations started happening to them? Combine giraffes to evolve them and discover their most curious, exotic and bizarre forms!

Just when you thought we had enough with Cow, Platypus and Goat Evolution, comes the sequel that takes the Evolution series to incredible new heights (tum dum tss). Giraffe Evolution!

All the cool stuff from the last games plus new features you can’t miss!
Hats? Aliens? Achievements? Leaderboards? It’s all here!

name: Train Sim World 3: Glossop Line - Manchester: Hadfield & Glossop Route
summary: Climb aboard the Northern Class 323 “Hyper Networker” and embark on a journey in Northwest England. Magnificent Mancunian scenery comes to life along the quaint Glossop Line: Manchester - Hadfield & Glossop in Train Sim World 3!

name: The Last Sunshine: Rekindled
summary: The Last Sunshine: Rekindled is a rogue-lite & schmup hybrid. Level up your stars, earn a variety of skills, then mix and match them with your customized stats to dispatch droves of dark aggressive enemies. Will light win against the darkness? It's the end of the universe!

name: OneDayOne
summary: OneDayOne - visual novel where you will dive into the routine life of Sergey, from which only a miracle and...your choices can help him escape

name: MiniMap Kingdom
summary: Build your own kingdom on unlimited mini maps!

name: Swan Princess Gator Escape
summary:
Simple Frogger clone. Features zero swans.

JeanBob is back to his old tricks... "I'm on a dangerous mission! A race to death!"

You control JeanBob by tapping as he is constantly on the move in the Swan Princess's kingdom. Hopping through the forest, in the castle, the town, he goes underground and underwater... while avoiding obstacles and collecting coins along the way.

name: Airhead Games
summary: Airhead Games is an AI-powered party game platform built to spark laughter, creativity, and a bit of friendly chaos. Featuring dynamic games and a witty AI host named Poppy, it's perfect for game nights and team bonding.

name: The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim - Legendary Edition
summary:
Live Another Life, In Another World: Play any type of character you can imagine, and do whatever you want; the freedom of choice, storytelling, and adventure of The Elder Scrolls comes to life in one legendary experience from all three official add-ons.

Dawnguard: The Vampire Lord Harkon has returned to power. By using the Elder Scrolls, he seeks to do the unthinkable - to end the sun itself. Will you join the ancient order of the Dawnguard and stop him? Or will you become a Vampire Lord?
Hearthfire: Purchase land and build your own home from the ground up - from a simple one-room cottage to a sprawling compound complete with an armory, alchemy laboratory, and more.

Dragonborn: Journey off the coast of Morrowind, to the vast island of Solstheim. Traverse the ash wastes and glacial valleys of this new land as you become more powerful with shouts that bend the will of your enemies and even tame dragons.

name: Chuchel: Cherry Edition
summary:
Cherry Edition contains the full game, 44-minute original soundtrack from the acclaimed band DVA and an 89-page digital art book with concepts and sketches by the creator Jaromir Plachy. "CHUCHEL Sans" OpenType font included. 
 
CHUCHEL is a comedy adventure game from the creators of Machinarium, Botanicula and Samorost. Join the hairy hero Chuchel and his rival Kekel as they will be facing numerous puzzles and challenges on their quest to retrieve the precious cherry!

name: King's Quest IV: The Perils of Rosella
summary: King's Quest IV: The Perils of Rosella is an adventure game in the King's Quest series. Players control Princess Rosella, daughter of King Graham, as she embarks on a quest to save her father's life and rescue a fairy kingdom. The game takes place in the land of Tamir, where Rosella must find a magical fruit to heal her ailing father while also helping the fairy queen Genesta reclaim her stolen talisman from the evil fairy Lolotte. Players navigate Rosella through various environments, solving puzzles and interacting with characters from folklore and fairy tales. King's Quest IV introduces real-time elements and day-night cycles to the series, affecting gameplay and puzzle solutions. The game expands on the series' narrative by focusing on a female protagonist and exploring new themes while maintaining the fantasy setting and puzzle-solving mechanics characteristic of the King's Quest franchise.

name: Battle Gear 2
summary: Take charge of military operations, enter enemy's territory from the air, sea and land, attack various parts of the world, battle for World Domination!

name: Mondealy: Day One
summary: Mondealy is about you building relationships and exploring the world. An ordinary guy from an ordinary town on an ordinary day uncovers the secrets of an extraordinary underground kingdom located under his home. Your adventure begins!

name: Neverending Light
summary: A guided tour goes horribly wrong when monsters eat everyone!

name: Approaching Infinity
summary: A sci-fi turn-based, tile-based Traditional Rogue-Like of incredible scope, accessible to new players, challenging to experienced rogue-likers. Explore an infinite procedural open-world universe full of unique environments as you lead your ship and crew to victory or death. Okay, mostly death.

name: Dragon Ball Z Tournament
